  "body": "The `MIN_VALIDATOR_WITHDRAWABILITY_DELAY` is applied twice:\r\n\r\n* In `prepare_validator_for_withdrawal()` it is included in `validator.withdrawable_epoch`.\r\n* In `process_exit_queue()` it is used for `eligible()`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<img width=\"457\" alt=\"screenshot 2019-03-01 at 15 36 19\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/731743/53644833-d1120e00-3c37-11e9-9432-40a787e1af7f.png\">\r\n",
